  <thing id="spS2IroCo4" name="Iron Construct" description="You transform an existing construct into a powerhouse of hardened iron, similar to the effect of the {i}iron body{/i} spell. The construct gains damage reduction 15/adamantine. It takes half damage from acid and fi re attacks of all kinds. Even if it is not a golem, however, it becomes vulnerable to all special attacks that affect iron golems.\n\nThe construct gains a +4 enhancement bonus to Strength, but takes a -4 penalty to Dexterity as well (to a minimum Dexterity of 1).\n\nThe construct&apos;s weight increases by a factor of five." compset="Spell">
