  <thing id="spS2ShLeg4" name="Shield of Faith, Legion&apos;s" description="This spell functions like {i}shield of faith{/i}, except that it affects multiple allies at a distance. \n\nThis spell creates a shimmering, magical field around the target that averts and deflects attacks. The spell grants the subject a +2 deflection bonus to AC, with an additional +1 to the bonus for every six levels you have (maximum +5 deflection bonus at 18th level)." compset="Spell">
