  <thing id="spS2ObsOb2" name="Obscure Object" description="This spell hides an object from location by divination (scrying) effects, such as the scrying spell or a crystal ball. Such an attempt automatically fails (if the divination is targeted on the object) or fails to perceive the object (if the divination is targeted on a nearby location, object, or person)." compset="Spell" summary="Masks object against scrying.">
