  <thing id="dS2Exorcis" name="Exorcism" description="You have the supernatural ability to force possessing spirits out of the bodies they inhabit. The possessing spirit makes a will save against the DC of your Channel Energy ability. Failure indicates you have forced the spirit out of the the body. If the spirit belongs to a spellcaster using {i}magic jar,{/i} the spirit returns to the receptacle. If it is a ghost or a possessing fiend, it becomes ethereal and free-floating again. In any case, the spirit cannot attempt to possess the same victim again for 24 hours.\n\n{b}Pathfinder{/b} Changed this to use the channel energy mechancis." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You have the supernatural ability to force possessing spirits out of the bodies they inhabit.">
